### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/libraries

### Get all libraries
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get library by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Create new library
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Biblioteca Central",
    "address": "Calle Principal 123"
}

### Update library
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Biblioteca Central Actualizada",
    "address": "Calle Principal 456"
}

### Delete library
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
